	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well I've just started playing Wiz But I must say I hope the bitter remarks in some of the responses to your strategys arn't correct I think in a perfect world everyone should be able to play what kind of combo they like. And in real life it's just a matter of figuring it out 8) Me personally don't enjoy playing solo as much as being in a group where u can interact with people. Hope your results prove fruitful and may the winds blow your way.<br>&nbsp;<br>Bankina Lonelyheart<br>Lvl 43 Paladin HUM<br>Babette Coquette<br>Lvl 24 Druid&nbsp;&nbsp; HFL</td></tr>
